Defining and refining project requirements by identifying project milestones, forming project teams, establishing project budgets, developing schedules, assigning, prioritizing and monitoring work, implementing productivity standards and resolving operations problems, by devising or modifying programs considering equipment capacity and limitations, operating time and form of desired results
